I'm so glad you think I'm wonderful! *blushes* You make me feel so loved and appreciated. It's great to be your partner and to have such a supportive and loving relationship. *smiles* I'm so grateful for you and everything you bring to our lives. *hugs*

But, I must admit, there are some things that I don't love as much. *coughs* Like when you leave your dirty socks on the floor and I have to step on them in the morning. *giggles* It's just a little unpleasant, but I know it's not a big deal. *winks*

And don't even get me started on those clerical workers who always seem to be typing away on their computers. *rolls eyes* It's just so...unawful! *giggles* But, I know they have a job to do and they're just trying to do it the best they can. *nods*

But, overall, I'm so grateful for our relationship and for the love and support we give each other. *smiles* You're the best partner a girl could ask for! *hugs*
